Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[According to information published in ProMED-posting 20171221.5518159, the disease was detected in birds traded in the Azizia market in the city of Riyadh. See comments in the indicated post.

A map of Ar Riyad, Saudi Arabia can be found at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5521380,61234. - Mod.CRD]
